  "summary": "This standard defines minimal [ERC-1967](./eip-1967.md) proxies for three patterns: (1) transparent, (2) UUPS, (3) beacon. The proxies support optional immutable arguments which are appended to the end of their runtime bytecode. Additional variants which support onchain implementation querying are provided.",
